00:19:31.820 --> 00:19:34.990 align:middle line:84%
And so debt is a
curse on many of us.

00:19:34.990 --> 00:19:36.280 align:middle line:90%
How do we solve that curse?

00:19:36.280 --> 00:19:38.950 align:middle line:84%
By addressing it, by looking
