00:19:38.950 --> 00:19:41.830 align:middle line:84%
with the emotional
neediness that

00:19:41.830 --> 00:19:43.810 align:middle line:90%
has brought us to that place.

00:19:43.810 --> 00:19:46.000 align:middle line:84%
And then creating a
practical plan for freedom

00:19:46.000 --> 00:19:49.232 align:middle line:84%
so that we can live in
freedom instead of in debt.

00:19:49.232 --> 00:19:53.290 align:middle line:84%
>> As a financial planner,
you're dealing with people

00:19:53.290 --> 00:19:55.800 align:middle line:84%
generally who have
a lot of money.

00:19:55.800 --> 00:19:57.250 align:middle line:84%
But there's somebody
out there who

00:19:57.250 --> 00:20:00.207 align:middle line:84%
is living from
paycheck to paycheck,

00:20:00.207 --> 00:20:02.290 align:middle line:84%
and his wife is working,
