00:20:07.270 --> 00:20:12.760 align:middle line:84%
If you could kind of sum up
all this type of planning,

00:20:12.760 --> 00:20:16.150 align:middle line:84%
give them some guidelines,
what would you tell them to do?

00:20:16.150 --> 00:20:20.890 align:middle line:10%
>> I think that the toughest
thing for a family like that is

00:20:20.890 --> 00:20:23.770 align:middle line:10%
to save, is to have a
relationship to money where

00:20:23.770 --> 00:20:26.260 align:middle line:10%
there's some saving and some
investing and some vision

00:20:26.260 --> 00:20:28.760 align:middle line:10%
of a future that is positive.

00:20:28.760 --> 00:20:32.860 align:middle line:84%
But if you think about it,
it's only about $6 a day

00:20:32.860 --> 00:20:35.020 align:middle line:84%
that is necessary
