00:21:08.795 --> 00:21:09.595 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

00:21:09.595 --> 00:21:11.320 align:middle line:90%
>> Just from compounding.

00:21:11.320 --> 00:21:15.640 align:middle line:84%
So it's just $5 or $6 a
