00:21:15.640 --> 00:21:17.350 align:middle line:84%
>> And what about
their credit card debt?

00:21:17.350 --> 00:21:18.250 align:middle line:90%
What would you say to them?

00:21:18.250 --> 00:21:20.260 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I think it's more
important to pay off the credit

00:21:20.260 --> 00:21:21.060 align:middle line:90%
