what you're actually earning.

00:21:27.850 --> 00:21:30.775 align:middle line:84%
And there's something
that's going to curse you

00:21:30.775 --> 00:21:31.650 align:middle line:90%
throughout your life.

00:21:31.650 --> 00:21:33.108 align:middle line:84%
If you're paying
all this interest,

00:21:33.108 --> 00:21:34.940 align:middle line:84%
