00:21:34.940 --> 00:21:36.920 align:middle line:90%
That doesn't buy you anything.

00:21:36.920 --> 00:21:40.240 align:middle line:84%
So if you can, instead of
having immediate gratification,

00:21:40.240 --> 00:21:42.430 align:middle line:84%
