delayed gratification,

00:21:42.430 --> 00:21:45.820 align:middle line:84%
you can in fact find a much
brighter future for you,

00:21:45.820 --> 00:21:46.855 align:middle line:90%
your family.

00:21:46.855 --> 00:21:49.420 align:middle line:84%
>> So there are two things
